item.title: CVE-2017-20144|2024-08-05T21:45:26.061Z -- anvsoft -- pdfmate%20pdf%20converter%20pro
item.description: A vulnerability has been found in Anvsoft PDFMate PDF Converter Pro 1.7.5.0 and classified as critical. The manipulation leads to memory corruption. The attack can be launched remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
